CatDescriptText: A broken door with a shattered glass window leads into a hallway with footprints on the floor.  There is a sled in the hallway of this residential building.  A staircase leads to the back.  The photograph may have been taken to record damages for an insurance claim.
TitMainTitle: Interior entryway of house with floral wallpaper and broken front door window, with sled in hallway in background, 6956 Upland Street, Homewood
